@startuml
title 购物车匿名→登录合并流程 (Cart Merge Sequence)

actor User as "买家"
participant APP as "APP/Web"
participant CartAPI as "Cart API"
participant CartMergeSvc as "CartMergeService"
participant LuaEngine as "Redis Lua Engine"
participant Redis as "Redis Cluster"
participant EventPub as "EventPublisher"

== 用户未登录, 加购 ==
User -> APP: 浏览商品, 加购
APP -> CartAPI: POST /api/v1/cart/items (deviceId, skuId, qty)
CartAPI -> LuaEngine: add_item.lua (anon_cart_id, sku, qty)
LuaEngine -> Redis: HSET cart:anon:{id}:items
LuaEngine -> Redis: ZADD cart:anon:{id}:sorted_set
Redis --> LuaEngine: success
LuaEngine --> CartAPI: {code:200}
CartAPI --> APP: 加购成功
APP --> User: 购物车已更新

== 用户登录, 触发合并 ==
User -> APP: 登录
APP -> CartAPI: POST /api/v1/cart/login (userId, deviceId)
CartAPI -> CartMergeSvc: merge(anonCartId, userCartId)

CartMergeSvc -> LuaEngine: merge_cart.lua (source=anon, target=user)
LuaEngine -> Redis: HGETALL cart:anon:{id}:items
Redis --> LuaEngine: 购物车行列表

loop 每行
    LuaEngine -> Redis: HEXISTS cart:user:{id}:items (sku:activity)
    alt 已存在同 SKU+活动
        LuaEngine -> Redis: 合并数量
    else 新 SKU
        LuaEngine -> Redis: HSET + ZADD
    end
end

LuaEngine -> Redis: DEL cart:anon:{id}:items
LuaEngine -> Redis: DEL cart:anon:{id}:sorted_set
LuaEngine -> Redis: DEL cart:anon:{deviceId}
Redis --> LuaEngine: 合并完成

LuaEngine --> CartMergeSvc: {code:200, merged_count}
CartMergeSvc -> EventPub: publish cart.merged (userId, merged_count)
EventPub -> Redis: 通知推送

CartMergeSvc --> CartAPI: 合并成功
CartAPI --> APP: 登录成功, 购物车已合并
APP --> User: 购物车已同步 (数量:N)

@enduml
